text: Josche Zurwonne (born 23 March 1989) is a German badminton player. He started playing badminton at age 8, and joined the Germany national badminton team in 2008. == Achievements == === BWF Grand Prix === The BWF Grand Prix has two levels, the Grand Prix and Grand Prix Gold.
